Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:04.11,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Alibis, codes, tricks, deals.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.11,0:00:06.23,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The mysterious Black Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:07.98,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's stage is an actual stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.98,0:00:09.98,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And behind the play lies a crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.69,0:00:13.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:15.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:41.99,Title,,0,0,0,,The Traveling Drama Troupe Murder Case (Part I)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teitan High
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:45.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What? You're the chairman of a drama troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:52.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tamanosuke Ito Troupe, Second Generation. Special performance of 'The Proclamation of the Successor'."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So you're moving up in your career!}So you play women's roles, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I guess. Before tonight's performance,}Actually, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.21,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Before the main piece tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:01.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke Ito (17)\NDrama Troupe Chairman
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{I want to dance 3 songs, changing clothes between each.}we'll be doing a traditional song show, where I will dance in drag on three pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going, I'm going! I won't miss this for anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah, what shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:14.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But comedians like you who\Ntravel through Japan are so lucky!}In a drama troupe, you get to travel all throughout Japan! It sounds incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. We usually do repeat performances every one or two years in the same place, to thank our fans.}Yeah, we do a tour through all the places our promoters ask us to go, lasting one or two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then, does that mean you've come to Beika Theater before?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But at the time my dad was the chairman, and I was just an actor. {So we didn't announce it as much.}So I wasn't as well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So your dad... died?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died a year ago from an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards, only half of the troupe remained.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.57,0:02:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to say it, but we've been through pretty bad times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:59.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll share these leaflets around! You can leave this to me, so just focus on practicing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's going to another school next month,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I want to cheer him on as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hoodwinked you, and now he wants to make you advertise for him, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{That's not it! Advertising is just an excuse! What I want is to see the backstage!}You're wrong! I'm the one who offered to advertise for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because I wanted him to let me see how they work backstage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! If you have so much time to waste, try to use it to study!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'll take Ran with me! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.88,0:03:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doesn't look very strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he's really handsome,\Nso he shouldn't be a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, if we get in trouble, you'll give him one of your kicks and that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{What's that supposed to mean? I'm not your bodyguard!}What are you saying?\NDon't act like I'm your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.64,0:03:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. Let's hurry and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:50.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:53.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.91,0:03:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:04:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't! We'd be a bother if we all went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I promise I'll take you there later during the first performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So be good little children!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be back before dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said to go through the personnel entry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could go through the main entrance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:20.76,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Beika Theater
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Let's go through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.59,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Maybe they're practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.31,0:04:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to bother you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all. You kids too, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:52.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We told you guys not to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you all came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? You're so kind, Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... This guy can do anything you ask of him: Ryuichi Muraki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuri Shirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, {the lead girl.}who plays the daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.09,0:05:15.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here to help distribute the leaflets. We're Sonoko and Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Muraki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, your {acting}action scenes were so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.59,0:05:21.76,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ryuichi Muraki (26)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nowadays, if you don't have special skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:22.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,the audience won't pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.97,0:05:26.22,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yuri Shirai (22)\NActress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.28,0:05:26.46,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it. I was only hired because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.46,0:05:29.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I was in the rhythm gymnastics club at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's hardly the {\i1}only{\i0} reason.\NSo cheer up, and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're going backstage, I'll talk to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, come up this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chairman, please hurry up with the script.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but could you wait a little longer, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Geez...}For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{We might as well have the theater closed tomorrow...}Good thing the theater's closed for a holiday tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:06:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm... We'll leave as soon as he's given us the leaflets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.47,0:06:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we practice with the new script later,\Neverything will work out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you have your first performance the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.88,0:06:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, our rental of the theater is running out,\Nso we don't have enough time to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This always happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:22.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:26.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are we doing a new show
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,instead of "Proclamation of the Successor" that we've been doing all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.23,0:06:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:39.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Megumi Ito (7)\NTamanosuke's Little Sister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm his little sister, Megumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My big brother is utterly daft,\Nso I have to do everything for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.42,0:06:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.28,0:06:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody's going crazy thanks to your crazy whims.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to be\Nplaying with pretty girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{We're only staying for a bit to pick up the leaflets.}We actually came here unannounced...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of these people then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:02.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you go take care of the final script, Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine, take them for a backstage visit, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.34,0:07:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.04,0:07:17.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, geez. Seems this really did turn completely upside down when his father died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it isn't Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:26.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! How do you know Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started going to Teitan Primary School today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're not in our class, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in Class C.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since he looks a lot like\Nbig brother when he was younger,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked my classmates what his name was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought I could be friends with Conan this quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But what are you doing standing there?}Well, first of all, I'll show you my room and the Chairman's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I'll show you the room I have here in the theatre!}I'll show you a photo of my brother when he was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys can come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:07:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who does she think she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cute... He's pretty popular with the girls, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't unpacked everything yet. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:15.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Doesn't he look like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, now... Where on Earth does {\i1}that{\i0} look like me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Ain't that a cross-dresser?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.23,Signs,,0,0,0,,okama
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,(male actor playing a female character)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.23,0:08:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an {\i1}oyama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.23,0:08:36.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true! He did look like Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would look so cute if he put on make-up like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, let's all go to everybody else's dressing rooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! Here, here, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.51,0:08:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kids are so innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me show them this, Itoe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.66,0:08:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itoe Ogiwara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is our accountant, though she's also an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.82,0:09:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Conan Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, his friends, and his big sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.02,0:09:08.55,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Itoe Ogiwara (28)\NActress and Accountant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:06.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.61,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please, come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm already done with my outfit, so I was just heading to the workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that kid your boyfriend, Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.57,0:09:18.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he's yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:25.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You got it wrong again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:38.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, let's hurry and go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be a good learning experience!\NWhy don't you try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.29,0:09:45.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you... What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making sure he knew our opinions diverged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.49,0:10:07.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. I-I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's with the scripts, Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.92,0:10:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're done. I'm printing them out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.79,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tetsuo Chikaishi (35)\NWriter for the Drama Troupe
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He told me to rewrite the last part,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,so I had to scare him a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{We have to teach him how life is while he's young, or he'll be useless once he's an adult.}If he doesn't understand how the world works when he's young,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{you can't expect to make any profit the next day.}he'll be useless once he's an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Tajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:38.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kenzo Tajima (45)\NActor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:39.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We'll be better off if everyone knows their place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm out of smokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, can you go buy another pack for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, I'll go buy the cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tajima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for this, Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.28,0:11:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megu, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why did you change the script from what we agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{The story is the story. And the drama is the drama. That's all I can say.}Reality is reality, and drama is drama. That's all I can say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine. {We'll do as you say.}We'll do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But we should start practicing right away.}We'll start reading the script right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.52,0:11:23.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:27.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the script's printed out, make copies for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until then, I'll be resting in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:40.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The chairman may be young, but {to treat him like that?}that's no excuse to be violent with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What the hell's wrong with this troupe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.83,0:11:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so cool! The sheets come one after the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, thanks for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The memoirs of Detective Itaro: The phantom thief, Edo Kid."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:10.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This phantom thief, the "Edo Kid"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. It's about the kid from the Edo era, about 400 years ago.}Yeah. The phantom thief from the Edo period that's become popular lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He's the protagonist in this story.}I used him as a model.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, boy. I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, {\i1}Sensei{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go and make the copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm finally done with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:33.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a nap now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are articles on the Edo Kid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was this Edo Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.71,0:12:48.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He's a thief who used to rob tons of places throughout Japan, especially Tokyo.}He showed up about half a year ago in Tokyo, and now he's acting in all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He lived like a thief from the old era, hopping through roofs, doing acrobatic leaps and the like.}He's like thieves from period dramas:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.45,0:12:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,escaping through the roofs and disappearing with acrobatic stunts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{The police called him the "ōedo Kid",}The police started calling him "Ōedo Kid{conan wiki: Flying Kid}" internally,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{but when the media started talking about him, they called him the "Edo Kid".}but it was leaked to the media, who called him "Edo Kid" and it stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.54,0:13:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister, did you pick Edo Kid as a model in the play
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you had actors capable of doing acrobatic stunts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, of course. Though sometimes the police suspected us.}Yeah, and because we also go on tour all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Those two even got interrogated\Nby the police at one point.}We were even suspected at one point and ended up being interrogated by the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really know what's up with our chairman,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{but I think he wanted to create\Na new version of the Edo Kid.}but making the new play on the Edo Kid is a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that why you've been investigating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of. When I put this in my computer, I always get his profile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Apparently your cute sister's here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys better go before I sock you a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for bothering you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you doing with someone who treated Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} so horribly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's resting in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was really affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{So, we're going home now.}So we're going out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have to hand out these leaflets, so come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were bothering them{Since you're here}, {you're gonna help us hand these out.}so we're going to help them advertise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that man from earlier went through that door down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{I think it's faster to go through the set.}Whether we go through there or through the set, we'll be pretty far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{But if we go this way, we'll be closer to the station.}But the backstage exit leaves us closer to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is she going to invite us to eat anything in the station?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it. It appears we're going to be assisting them in delivering leaflets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:39.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll invite you to something, so hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! A boxed eel lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you in advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:06.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10I'm sure there's something hiding behind those people.}I'm sure those people are hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:15.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{How many times have we told you not to ditch us, Conan?}You know better than to ditch us, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:16.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.89,0:15:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to handing out the leaflets?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.03,0:15:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old lady who works for a community just took them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.79,0:15:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Conan, you're not gonna fool us.}Conan, we can cheat just as well as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanted to {lose us and }go back to the theater, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. You really do earn the name "Detective Boys"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right! I thought you'd gone back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look! Do I look good? We're gonna start\Nrehearsing now! Cheer me on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's the chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine. Sorry about what happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you look great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're playing Itaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since the act's short, if you want, you can stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look! Look at her!{There's a house there!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a samurai movie on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.69,0:16:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What's that hole doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's an exit platform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want to fall in that hole!\NIt's very deep and dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.48,0:16:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the thief! So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1 minute and 40 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.99,0:16:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes too long for you to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.61,0:17:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he goes behind the curtain,\Ndown the stairs while changing clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then goes back out that way,\Nit's like a really cool magic trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he takes too long because he doesn't have anyone to help him change his clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop {talking about the troupe's secrets,}telling them about our problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and show your friends where they can sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These seats are the most central ones,\Nand where you can get the best view.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, don't you have to practice, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't go home. Stay here and watch, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right! See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I wonder what Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} changed in the last scene in the script...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:42.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After doing the first rehearsal, they've been repeating it over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:45.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10"The Memoirs of Detective Itarō".}"The Chronicles of Itaro's Arrest".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A story about Edo-era detective Itaro,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and his little sister, his assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:54.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Together, they deduced the identity of{ Japan's number one thief,} the Edo Kid, a thief who's been stealing throughout all of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:57.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This leads them to suspect that one of the members of a theater troupe is the real Edo Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:02.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but after they try to arrest him, they find out that the real Edo Kid is someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.79,0:18:06.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Apparently, the true criminal was actually the twin brother of the actor they tried to arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.01,0:18:11.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then, the troupe goes on another tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Though the title is "The Chronicles of Itaro's Arrest",
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:19.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}it's odd that the main character, Itaro, got the criminal wrong in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, how was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were great!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was great, Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I take some juice to my friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guys, wait a bit for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, Megu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to figure out some of the last details, so can you call Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.51,0:18:50.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}! {\i1}Sensei{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still asleep? I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.33,0:18:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei{\i0}, wake u—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megumi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.03,0:19:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was hit in the head from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems the murder weapon was this empty jar...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Someone please call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:31.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:36.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:38.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why is he so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is he just that restless?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:41.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The floppy disk is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, big brother? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.36,0:20:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:15.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something missing? The room looks like it was ransacked...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:23.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's with this guy? Why won't he say that the floppy's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is the troupe's script-writer, Tetsuo Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 35 years old, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.32,0:20:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried because I didn't know where you were, so I came here to see if you'd come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez... It's always the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:53.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Greetings, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{They say he died about an hour ago.}Time of death seems to have been about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.78,0:21:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Sounds like a job for my agency, huh?}There's a chance the killer was someone from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you all an hour ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.04,0:21:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were all practicing for the play!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:17.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We were watching the play\Nand saw everything they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And being a general practice,{is "dress rehersal" the right term? -uso.} even those without parts were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:25.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only time we lost sight of them was when they went to change clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.16,0:21:29.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Then when the platform was used, there was only one person working?}Then, when he went up on the platform, he was alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{He's the only theater employee who came to work today.}Besides that, today we also have the theater's technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:44.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somebody beat Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} to death, stole the floppy, then came back to the stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:46.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.04,0:21:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Inspector, you have to find the missing floppy disk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chikaishi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had it on the\Ntable with the script, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.48,0:21:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:21:59.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why did he hide this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:03.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's possible that he killed him and someone else stole the floppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:07.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or is he covering up for the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:11.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Still, the killer is one of the people here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.19,0:23:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.03,0:23:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Itoe{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.79,0:24:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the forensic report, that note was definitely written by Tamanosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.92,0:24:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tamanosuke{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.18,0:24:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer is someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.05,0:24:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: "The Traveling Drama Troupe Murder Case (Part II)"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Script
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.55,0:24:20.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time, it's December already!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.82,0:24:22.82,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,So, this year's almost over?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.44,0:24:24.13,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
